            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td bgcolor="#f4f4f4" align="center" style="padding: 0px 10px 0px 10px">
        <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="max-width: 600px">
          <tr>
            <td bgcolor="#ffffff" align="left" style="
                  color: #000000;
                  font-family: 'Poppins', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
                  font-size: 15px;
                  font-weight: 400;
                  line-height: 25px;
                  text-align: left;
                ">
              <p style="margin: 10px 40px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 500">
                Hey there,
              </p>
              <p style="margin: 2px 40px">
                Excited to have you join WorkPlay!
              </p>
              <p style="margin: 0px 40px">
                Let's kick things off by verifying your email. Just hit the
                button below:
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td bgcolor="#ffffff" align="left">
              <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
                <tr>
                  <td bgcolor="#ffffff" align="center" style="padding: 30px 0px 20px 0px">
                    <table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
                      <tr>
                        <td align="center" style="border-radius: 3px" bgcolor="#FFA73B">
